{"id":"shemiramoth","term":"Shemiramoth","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Most high name. (1.) A Levite in the reign of Jehoshaphat (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Chronicles 17:8\">2 Chr. 17:8</a>).</p>\n<p>(2.) A Levite in David’s time (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 15:18\">1 Chr. 15:18</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 15:20\">20</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Chronicles 17:8","1 Chronicles 15:18","1 Chronicles 15:20"]}